          <p>The Explore portion of AntLab allows users to see specimens that have been collected from their area. The user enters the name of a city; the site uses the geocoder gem to convert this city to a latitude and longitude and then returns samples collected near this area. Samples are returned via an API request to <a href="http://www.antweb.org/">antweb.org</a>.</p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/explorations" role="button">View &raquo;</a></p>
